00:03:01.391 --> 00:03:03.741
So it's going to be one over

00:03:03.741 --> 00:03:05.509
the natural log of four.

00:03:05.509 --> 00:03:07.015
The natural log of four.

00:03:07.015 --> 00:03:09.291
